Murderball 2013 README

Implemented Features:
- Basic game structure: AnimatedSprite class, updates/draws, input, etc.
- Players: Class, input, collision detection.
- Balls: Class, physics, collision detection.

To implement:
- Balls: Particle effects
- Players: Hitpoints, animations for rolling, getting hit.
- Title screen graphics
- Improved sounds: bounces, hits, explosions
- Title screen music and match music

Possible future options: 
- Multiple character select
- Random traps and extra balls during matches
- Robot 'referee'
- In-match txt commentary

